---
title: Irish Sirloin Steak in Hoisin Sauce with rice, pickled radish and pan-fried greens
description: East meets West in this indulgent dish. Traditionally Asian elements such as pickled radish, jasmine rice and hoisin sauce accompany 21-day-aged 100% Irish sirloin steak and tender veg for an unexpectedly delicious recipe.
